# 🛒 Production-Ready E-Commerce Backend System

## 📌 Overview

This is a scalable and secure e-commerce backend system built to simulate real-world online shopping platforms. It handles user authentication, product management, order processing, and payment integration using industry-standard backend practices.

The system is designed with maintainability, scalability, and security in mind, following a clean MVC architecture.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

- 🔐 JWT-based Authentication & Authorization
- 👥 Role-Based Access Control (Admin/User)
- 🛍 Product Management System
- ☁️ Product Image Upload on Cloudinary
- 📦 Order Processing & Tracking
- 💳 Payment Gateway Integration
- 🧱 MVC Architecture
- ⚙️ Environment-based Configuration (.env)
- ❌ Centralized Error Handling
- 🔒 Secure Password Hashing

---

## 🧱 System Architecture

This project follows the MVC (Model-View-Controller) pattern:

- **Controllers** → Handle HTTP requests and responses
- **Services** → Business logic layer
- **Models** → Database interactions

This separation ensures scalability and clean code organization.

---

## 📡 API Endpoints (Sample)

### 🔐 Auth

- POST `/api/auth/register`
- POST `/api/auth/login`

### 🛍 Products

- GET `/api/products`
- POST `/api/products` (Admin)

### 📦 Orders

- POST `/api/orders`
- GET `/api/orders`

### 👑 Admin

- GET `/api/admin/users`
- DELETE `/api/admin/user/:id`

---

## 🔥 Key Highlights

- Designed as a real-world backend system
- Implements secure authentication flows
- Includes payment processing logic
- Demonstrates clean architecture and scalability
- Uses environment variables for security

---

## 🌍 Real-World Relevance

This project reflects how modern e-commerce platforms manage users, products, payments, and orders securely. It demonstrates backend engineering practices used in production environments.

