## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ecommerce-backend-system.git
cd ecommerce-backend-system
npm install
```

---

## 🔐 Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file:

```
PORT=5000
DATABASE_URL=your_db_url
JWT_SECRET=your_secret
PAYMENT_KEY=your_payment_key
```

---

## ▶️ Run Project

```bash
npm start
```

